Building a rocket first requires constructing a <link=\"LAUNCHPAD\">Rocket Platform</link> and adding modules from the menu. All components of the Rocket Checklist will need to be complete before being capable of launching.\n\nA <link=\"CLUSTERTELESCOPE\">Telescope</link> needs to be built on the surface of a Planetoid in order to use the <style=\"KKeyword\">Starmap Screen</style> {Hotkey/ManageStarmap} to see and set course for new destinations.